{"tid":2140741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"何栢良為甚麼要道歉？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-05T07:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:08:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88419bcd5256c242c2350d5d9f169713d399e5f4","tid":2140741,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/U6SARGNCENDJDJ6GBPIGW75464/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FU6SARGNCENDJDJ6GBPIGW75464%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZealKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=dabddcba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FU6SARGNCENDJDJ6GBPIGW75464%2F&h=318550c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/U6SARGNCENDJDJ6GBPIGW75464/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n何栢良為甚麼要道歉？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cuZFUc8fclraXm5sxJPXa0HAlA4=/793x444/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3WA7XNYUDNDIRJLG3J4BY2FW4Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcuZFUc8fclraXm5sxJPXa0HAlA4%3D%2F793x444%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3WA7XNYUDNDIRJLG3J4BY2FW4Y.png&h=71eacb4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n餐廳禁止堂食令推出後，怨聲載道，結果實施了兩天便草草結束。<br />\n<br />\n一個政府，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良為甚麼要道歉？<br />\n<br />\n原來，何栢良。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫生或醫學專家從醫學及公共衛生角度提出禁堂食建議，有甚麼問題呢？。。。。。。。。。。。擾民的不是禁止堂食，而是在不封關、免檢疫、工繼續返的情況下禁止堂食。<br />\n<br />\n外國很多國家都曾禁止食肆堂食，以加拿大為例，政府向所有受影響食肆提供補償，也向居家抗疫、失去收入的民眾提供每月2000加幣的收入補償。這筆錢迄今仍在發放。<br />\n<br />\n香港的混亂局面由港府一手造成，既然工不停，巿民就要外出工作，既然外出工作，就要在外面吃午餐。全港打工仔被一個午餐搞得尊嚴盡喪，政府憑甚麼不道歉？<br />\n<br />\n而且，政府甚麼時候把專家的專業意見放在眼裏了？醫護團體幾個月前便強烈要求政府封關，政府聽了嗎？專家認為免檢疫措施存在漏洞，政府聽了嗎？如果一早聽取專業意見，香港的疫情早已受控。"},{"pid":"953933ad4444f451c1aa01d3139152d016e643b2","tid":2140741,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef02aa15412d3c4a8bc23043babbee73ea548c82","tid":2140741,"uid":11738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5eabed98d40d62901f8987be56dc1493ce37e530","tid":2140741,"uid":328267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"根本個問題就係好多公司冇提供藍領應有嘅休息地點，<br />\n而政府係有法例監管但冇去做，<br />\n之前已經爆過幾單新聞政府外判清潔工要喺廁所同垃圾站食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次全日禁堂食只係導火線，咁啱引爆政府仆街無能嘅炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}